show.name: Вампиры средней полосы
show.summary: Grandpa Slava is the oldest of the Midland vampire family. They live quietly. They live by the law. They live the unremarkable life of an ordinary Russian family and they never kill humans – ever. Although, of course, everyone knows they drink blood. And when some lifeless corpses are found in a birch grove near Smolensk... their peaceful life falls under threat.

show.name: Мартышкины
show.summary: Each family monkeys in its own way! Such different and such friendly Monkeys live in the center of a highly eco-friendly metropolis, surrounded by clever gadgets. Every day is a new adventure, in which there is a place for children's imagination and light hooliganism. Each new episode is one day of the life of big and small monkeys, something very monkey-like happens to them, but similar to human life.

show.name: Wu Shen Zhu Zai
show.summary:
The protagonist Qin Chen, who was originally the top genius in the military domain, was conspired by the people to fall into the death canyon in the forbidden land of the mainland. Qin Chen, who was inevitably dead, unexpectedly triggered the power of the mysterious ancient sword.

Three hundred years later, in a remote part of the Tianwu mainland, a boy of the same name accidentally inherited Qin Chen's will. As the beloved grandson of King Dingwu of the Daqi National Army, due to the birth father's birth, the mother and son were treated coldly in Dingwu's palace and lived together. In order to rewrite the myth of the strong man in hope of the sun, and to protect everything he loves, Qin Chen resolutely took up the responsibility of maintaining the five kingdoms of the world and set foot on the road of martial arts again.

show.name: Wan Jie Du Zun
show.summary: Lin Feng was gathering his martial soul in the Lin Mansion. He didn't want to. His fiancee Ji Manyao took the opportunity to take his martial soul, and he almost vomited blood and died. At the same time, Lin Feng's spirit entered the land of the burial of the gods. The mysterious woman in the land of the burials told Lin Feng that he could gain enormous martial arts power and knowledge by obliterating the ancient gods buried here.

show.name: Forty Millenniums of Cultivation
show.summary: "Even if this universe is truly nothing more than a brutal bloody shadowy forest, we Cultivators will burn all that we have just to give off a single weak flickering spark in the darkness! "No matter how weak each spark is, how short-lived, how small… As long as the sparks flow unabated, then one day one of those sparks will light some tinder, and that tinder shall light some fallen branches, and those branches shall set ablaze each and every last tree of the forest! "In the end, even the smallest sparks will eventually set the shadowy forest ablaze and illuminate the whole world!" (NovelUpdate) In a world teeming with cultivators, Li Yao, who makes his living collecting scrap metal, encounters the soul of a titan powerhouse from forty thousand years in the past.

show.name: Leveling up in a Fantasy World
show.summary: When he opened his eyes, he was in a different world, and he was bound by a simple system that told him that world domination was no longer a dream! Is there such a good thing? Qin Huai gave in and became a 007 working boy in the other world, earning points day and night, and the result was, of course, real! The divine weapons, the treasures, the supreme techniques and the gentle and lovely little sister, all of them come to his arms!

show.name: Drawing Jianghu: The Degenerate
show.summary:
Adapted from the anime "The Degenerate-Drawing Jianghu" (画江湖之不良人) by Beijing Ruosen Digital Technology Co., Ltd. (北京若森数字科技有限公司).

In the last years of the Tang Dynasty, the world was in turmoil, and the vassal towns were divided into two groups. It is said that before the Huangchao rebels captured Chang'an, the mysterious organization of the government had carried out its last mission and disappeared. Almost at the same time as they disappeared, there was also the famous treasure that the rebels searched all over Chang'an but could not find. Since then, a rumor has spread in the world that there is a big secret hidden on the legendary Longquan sword. Until one day, a mysterious orphan named Li Xing Yun was rescued by the hermit Uncle Yang by chance, and worked under him to learn martial arts. A few years later, Li Xing Yun and his sister Lu Lin Xuan went down the mountain to practice martial arts. On their way, they met two friends, Ji Ru Xue and Zhang Zi Fan, and then happened to get the legendary Longquan sword. As a result, Li Xing Yun and Longquan Sword have aroused the covetousness of many sects including Xuanmingjiao, Tongwenguan, Huanyinfang and Tianshifu.

show.name: Drawing Jianghu: The Degenerate
show.summary:
Adapted from the anime "The Degenerate-Drawing Jianghu" (画江湖之不良人) by Beijing Ruosen Digital Technology Co., Ltd. (北京若森数字科技有限公司).

show.name: Ling Jian Zun
show.summary: The strong man was attacked and returned to his youth. He became the weakest waste young lord. He will never let go of the enemy of the previous life in this life and must make up the regret of the previous life in this life! By the time the Spirit Sword is powerful, the protagonist will be supreme in the three worlds between heaven and earth! If there is someone doesn't obey him, he will kill him with the sword!

show.name: Hi Venus
show.summary: As a pediatrician working at the Taoyuan Village Clinic, Ye Shi Lan has nothing but the best interest of her patients at heart. Wanting only the best for the children she treats, Shi Lan should have been happy when the new hospital director, Lu Zhao Xi, was appointed. But a rather large misunderstanding on her part means she and the new director start their working relationship off on the very wrong foot. Believing Zhao Xi is an unscrupulous drug dealer who has no qualms about defrauding people, Shi Lan does everything she can to make the new hospital director's life miserable. But after she's appointed to the position of his temporary assistant, it doesn't take long for her to realize she was terribly mistaken about Zhao Xi. Working closely together to solve a number of problems, Shi Lan and Zhao Xi are eventually able to put the past behind them and begin to develop a mutual understanding and respect for each other. Working side-by-side to save lives, Zhao Xi and Shi Lan gain a deeper understanding of what it means to be a doctor. Inspiring each other to become the best they can be, this unlikely pair begin to fall in love but are either of them ready to admit the feelings they've secretly been harboring?

What is hidden in this small village?

show.name: Large Queen
show.summary: Su Jinxia, the daughter of the Great General, was appointed as the Empress consort of the sickly old Emperor. Unfortunately, on the wedding day, the old Emperor passed away. Upon hearing the news that she was to be buried together with the old Emperor, Su Jinxia collapsed. Her body was then taken over by the soul of a fashion designer from modern times. This new Su Jinxia was different from the original one. She was bold and cheerful. The new Emperor spared her from the sacrificial burial as long as she was willing to marry him. So she became the Empress consort of the new Emperor. Unaware of the Emperor's true love, Su Jinxia eventually ran away from the palace. When this plump Empress consort learned that fat women were considered low in status and bullied outside, she decided to open a plus-size clothing store. Soon, the Emperor appeared to pursue his love.

show.name: Warning Ahead
show.summary: It tells the story of the ruthless killer Jiang Li, who took root in Shanghai under her anonymity in order to avenge her family for many years. She married Shen Shi You, the owner of a trading company. The two of them live harmoniously, and their love increases, but they are unintentionally involved in more lies and conspiracies... The two confront each other, and the lover becomes the enemy. They are the sweetest couple, but also the strongest opponents. They are evenly matched, falling in love and killing each other.

name: Familieselskap
summary: When the extended family from the country and the beach gathers, it can result in complete dialect confusion. Today, it is important to understand as much as possible.

show.name: 24-stjerners julekalender
show.summary: Markus has gathered 24 celebrities to compete in the Christmas strip's biggest challenges. Who is left as this year's Christmas star? Norwegian reality Christmas calendar.

show.name: Çekiç ve Gül: Bir Behzat Ç. Hikayesi
show.summary: After graduating from the Police Academy in 1985, Behzat starts working in the Ankara Police Department Murder Bureau. He is fearless, intelligent, strong and charismatic. Behzat remains a detective, while all his colleagues move to higher positions. Although he always gets into trouble, he has his own methods of catching criminals. He is constantly referred to the disciplinary committee, but will never change. Behzat does not trust anyone, especially women.. Behzat does not follow the rules, he creates his own rules.

show.name: The Legend of Young Justice Bao
show.summary: The story tells about various bizarre mysteries such as "Blood Soul Forest," "Pouling Town," and "Ghost Valley" that Bao Zheng experienced in his youth on his way to Beijing to rush to the exam.

show.name: Bride of the Typhoon
show.summary: The story of a woman who became the daughter-in-law of an enemy for desperate revenge.

name: Gebrochene Versprechen
summary: The department store Jonass has changed from a credit to a luxury department store - and Vicky is promoted to department manager. A lot has happened in her private life too: She is the mother of three-year-old Hanni and has a new partner at her side in Wilhelm, who is now even proposing to her. Harry and Helene are returning from the States where they have been for the past three years. Helene has accepted a position at the Charité and Harry has decided to get a record deal. But back home, Harry longs for Vicky. In recent years she has never answered his letters. Still, his feelings for her haven't changed...

show.name: Das Haus der Träume
show.summary: Berlin in the 1920's. A dazzling place, but times are not only golden, they are marked by poverty and crime. Vicky arrives in the city, led by promises of a better life, she's looking for a job. But as soon as she gets there, her hopes and dreams are met with a cold awakening. With no place to stay and nothing to her name, she hires on to work as a saleswoman at a newly-established, glamorous department store. But the founders are also fighting for survival, just like Vicky. Times are tough, and it's about to get tougher.

show.name: Krucjata
show.summary: This contemporary police procedural drama is a suspenseful action series focusing on the investigations conducted by Detective Jan 'Manjaro' Góra and his colleagues from the Crime and Criminal Terror Division of the Warsaw Metropolitan Police. They investigate a series of murders and kidnappings of celebrities - an influential TV journalist, a judge in a talent show, a banker, and an MP. At first glance, the cases are not linked. However, it soon turns out that all the tragic events are arranged into a much larger and more complicated whole. Behind these crimes stands an anti-system terrorist organization operating in Warsaw.

show.name: It's Like a Bean in a Pod
show.summary: A bad daughter-in-law appeared in a 30-year-old traditional Gomtang restaurant. The second love of Yeong-i, a single mother who speaks her mind no matter what, and the story of many families.

show.name: The Guardian
show.summary: Post 90s police cadets Wang Ji Xiang, Luo Xin and Zhang Miao Miao have been assigned to the Yong Cheng Xin Qiao Police Station after graduation. However, Luo Xin accidentally causes the death of a mentally handicapped girl and receives a 2-year prison sentence. With the police station in a crisis, Chen Xiao Jing is set to take over as the new director. Wang Ji Xiang works hard to rectify their name while Zhang Miao Miao finds that a way to engage and help the masses through webcasting. Together with their fellow officers, they aim to bring the police station to its former glory.

show.name: The Shop
show.summary: The Shop gives viewers a one-of-a-kind barbershop experience, which for many provides a sanctuary for free-flowing and spirited discussions. The series will visit barbershops around the country to gather distinguished individuals who can speak honestly on sports, music, pop culture, world events, business and other culturally relevant topics.

name: Holiday Mailbag!
summary: Jon, Jon and Dan answer all of your burning questions about 2024, the Democratic party, the White Lotus, Taylor Swift, and more.

show.name: Pod Save America
show.summary: Pod Save America is a no-bullshit conversation about politics hosted by former Obama aides Jon Favreau, Jon Lovett, Dan Pfeiffer, and Tommy Vietor. It cuts through the noise to break down the week's news and helps people figure out what matters and how they can help. They're regularly joined by journalists, activists, politicians, entertainers, and world leaders. You can listen to new episodes twice a week on Tuesdays and Thursdays.

show.name: 10 глупых вопросов
show.summary: Do you want to learn more about modern and interesting professions, but you are afraid to ask a stupid question? We will ask stupid questions to professionals for you. And they will tell you how everything really is. You are watching 10 stupid questions.

name: Почему Латвия, Литва и Эстония — самые жесткие противники Москвы? / Редакция контекст
summary:
There is a term "complex issues" in the lexicon of diplomacy. These are long-standing conflicts and painful problems in relations between countries and peoples. These are the "difficult issues" that make up Russia's relations with the Baltic states.

On the one hand, this is the history of their accession to the USSR during Stalin's time. On the other hand, the problem of the rights of the Russian-speaking minority. Recent events have only aggravated everything — Latvia, Lithuania and Estonia occupy the toughest position among the EU countries. The story of the "Rain"* is another confirmation. 

In general, it's time to figure out — why did this happen? And where will this neighborhood lead?

show.name: Редакция
show.summary: The author's journalistic program of Alexey Pivovarov, where he asks questions and interviews guests, makes reports on actual themes, as well as on entertaining topics.

show.name: Книга-мандрівка. Україна
show.summary:
First Ukrainian cartoon series based on real events and unreal adventures of Ukrainians — the Travelbook. Ukraine.

Why a "book"? Because the series was created on the basis of the bestselling book, the Travelbook. Ukraine from creative agency Green Penguin Media, and now the characters, stories and discoveries have come to life on Ukrainian YouTube!

How can a Ukrainian decipher the script of an ancient Mayan civilization without leaving the office? Why should you never challenge a Nobel prize winner to a duel? Who helped Mykola Gogol create the first Ukrainian fantasy? How did the Ukrainian woman change the world of ballet fashion and receive an Oscar?

name: Hall & Oates John Oates: Wake Up Call
summary: John Oates (Hall & Oates) joins us this week to share his experience in the music industry and the ups and downs that come with being in a Rock & Roll Hall of Fame inducted, multi million record selling duo like Hall & Oates. John opens up on how he was able to pull himself out of the spiral his life was in during the late 80's as he wanted to change his image, was dealing with a divorce, and found out that he was being hoodwinked by Wall Street money managers. We also get into the mental health messaging that John includes in his music, who he was most excited to perform with, and some unfortunate things to happen on stage while he was performing.

show.name: Inside of You with Michael Rosenbaum
show.summary: Inside of You with Michael Rosenbaum is a podcast, recorded series inside of the home of Michael Rosenbaum (Sorority Boys, Smallville). Listen as he invites celebrities, athletes, musicians, or anyone he finds interesting to sit next to on the couch, while he probes them for the most interesting stories they have.

show.name: All Elite Wrestling: Dark
show.summary: All Elite Wrestling: Dark features the matches you didn't see on All Elite Wrestling: Dynamite.

name: Nazis: Neo-pagans?
summary: Books, films, and comics are filled with Nazi scientists and explorers travelling the globe to get their hands on ancient artifacts or summoning daemons with black magic. But how much of it is grounded in reality? Well, some of it. In the neo-pagan religion invented by Reichsführer-SS Heinrich Himmler, the world can only be explained through the occult.

show.name: World War Two: Week by Week
show.summary: World War Two dives into the history of one of the most devastating wars in human history. Indy Neidell, Spartacus Olsson and their team of dedicated historians cover the events of World War Two week by week in realtime. Additionally, we take an in-depth look at the war against humanity, key figures in all camps, military hardware, impact on culture, military strategies and life at the home fronts or under occupation.

name: TayNew Meal Date in Japan Part 2
summary: For their second episode in Yokohama, Japan, Tay and New share a meal at a delicious Japanese restaurant.

show.name: TayNew Meal Date
show.summary: Follow Tay and New as they explore the local foods of Thailand at the end of every month on their meal date.

name: The Curse of the Clawback
summary: While everyone is dressing their part, there's still work that needs to get done. Lindsey is continuing to push the accounting team to the brink with her continuous discovery of control deficiencies, and finding of outlandish terms in the sales teams contracts, which could lead to the dreaded: clawback! Meanwhile Sarah and Hunter, not so subtlety, hash out their ongoing passive aggressive relationship battle as Marty continues to be his punny self. For Makayla, she has bigger fish to fry: her reputation. After a Tweet threating to expose and cancel her puts her on edge, she is on a mission to get ahead of the publicity before it's too late.

show.name: PBC
show.summary: Sarah is just trying to "be audit she can be". After finally quitting her job at a major public firm, Sarah finds herself as the Senior Accountant for SUNRYZER A.I., a fast-track to IPO tech start-up that is preparing for their annual year-end audit. While she's trying to make a good impression, her new accounting team of Hunter and Makayla isn't making it easy for her to focus on work. Meanwhile she doesn't get much support from her Manager Tracy, Controller Dave, or CFO Jessica. On top of all her normal work duties, she finds herself caught up in workplace drama thanks to top-notch auditor Lindsey and a nosey janitor. This workplace comedy sheds light onto the hilarious scenarios CPAs, staff accountants, and audit professionals find themselves in on a daily basis.

summary: Matched couples finally learn each others' age and profession. Back at the Inferno, disappointed singles take time to reflect on the events of the day.

show.name: Single's Inferno
show.summary: Stranded and ready to mingle, flirty singles search for love on a deserted island they can only escape as couples for romantic date nights in paradise.

name: Episode 4
summary: A charismatic newcomer captures Shin Seul-ki's attention. For the second couple selection, some follow their heart while others seek someone new.

show.name: Single's Inferno
show.summary: Stranded and ready to mingle, flirty singles search for love on a deserted island they can only escape as couples for romantic date nights in paradise.

show.name: First Love
show.summary:
Lu Wanwan is a sophomore in the Clinical Department of Qingyao University School of Medicine. However, her poor psychological quality makes Lu Wanwan easy to perform abnormally during exams, and she is out of tune with the strict medical school. Due to the failure of secret love for many years, Lu Wanwan threatened to pursue Ren Chu, the super school leader of the same school, after drinking, and the scandal between the two came out. The uproaring scandal has seriously affected Lu Wanwan's already struggling study life. In order to separate the relationship between the two, Lu Wanwan managed to sign the 'Gossip Elimination Plan' with Ren Chu. In the process of clarifying the scandal, the two slowly saw the shining points in each other's characters, and gradually developed a good feeling for each other. With the help and guidance of Ren Chu, Lu Wanwan gradually overcame her inner timidity, found a balance between her interests and studies, and worked hard to become a qualified medical student. Ren Chu was also infected by Lu Wanwan and got rid of her studies. The tyrannical arrogance is becoming more and more friendly. Both of them were unconsciously changed by each other and became a better version of themselves, and finally gained a healthy and independent campus romance.

Adapted from the novel "Chu Ci Ai Ni, Wei Shi Bu Wan" (初次爱你，为时不晚) by Zhun Ni Jia Qi (准拟佳期).

summary: RJ finally returns to work at the bar. Bai Lang meets Jin Xun An's family.

show.name: My Tooth Your Love
show.summary:
Bai Lang is a bar-restaurant owner with an all-too-familiar phobia. Ever since he was a young child, he has dreaded having to go to the dentist. And although he has tried countless times to change dentist in search of someone who does not fill him with dread, nothing frightens him more than the idea of having to have his teeth checked. But all that changes on the day that he visits the Gao Leng Dental Hospital – and meets the hospital's chief dentist Jin Xun'an.

Jin Xun'an is not like all the dentists that Bai Lang has met before. He is gentle, caring, and kind. And Bai Lang begins to feel that Jin Xun'an sees him as more than a patient – and has romantic feelings toward him. But can love really spark between a dentist and his patient? Meanwhile, Zhou Cheng Hao a senior bartender at Bai Lang's bar and the owner's close friend is developing a close relationship with He Qing Tian – a rebellious young man 12 years his junior. Many obstacles stand in the way of love for this quartet – but will Cupid find a way to bring happiness to them all?

name: Jungwoo
summary: Time passes by and Jungwoo returned to his daily routine. He is trying to live well by himself without Choco and Milk.

show.name: Choco Milk Shake
show.summary: Two strange men just barge in through the doors one day. They say that they are 'Choco', Jungwoo's childhood pet dog and 'Milk', his childhood cat. Can Jungwoo trust these weird and handsome men? A grand operation to find my love with my pet who came back crossing the rainbow bridge.

The Ukraїner team went on an expedition through the already liberated territories to record incredible stories of resistance and modern partisanship.

show.summary:
Adapted from the novel "Ben Yue" (奔月) by Shu Ke (蜀客).
Young Liu Shao meets a mysterious man with whom she exchanges her future for three full days of happiness. Initially, she has led the carefree life of an heiress until she became embroiled in the battle between the immortals and the demons. Her involvement leads to the unravelling of several romantic entanglements between herself and Lu Li, the cloaked immortal shrouded in mystery.

show.name: PLA Air Force
show.summary: Air Force Captain Qin Lang overcame difficulties in a live-fire exercise and completed the task, but was sent to refit the air tanker. Qin Lang, who wanted to refit the K-type aircraft, refused to obey but had to obey the orders of his superiors. In Jiangcheng, Qin Lang met Feng Lei, an air force colonel who was dismissed due to an accident. Feng Lei, who was rigorous and inhumane, and Qin Lang, who was arrogant and emotional, had a great conflict in concept. The two often battled wits and courage during training. . In an accident, Feng Lei found that Qin Lang had a serious psychological shadow on the right-hand parking in the air. Feng Lei tried various methods to make Qin Lang overcome his psychological fear regardless of his previous suspicions. Neighboring countries were in turmoil, but our army went abroad to counter terrorism but encountered terrorist attacks. The plane was hit by enemy missiles. Qin Lang overcame his psychological fear and landed in a single round to save the people and the plane. In the end, Qin Lang refitted the K-type machine as he wished, and also gained love. The captain Feng Lei also re-understood family, friendship and love in his relationship with Qin Lang.

show.name: Way Back Into Love
show.summary:
The action takes place in the future world of science and technology.

This is the story of Fan Jian Jian, a wife who, in order to help her husband Lu Ze, who was in a car accident and fell into a coma, turned to brain expert Dr. Sun for help and took part in an experiment with a brain and a computer.

With the help of technology, she penetrates into the brain of her lover, and in order to save him, she must relive three important memories for both of them.

show.summary: This is a reality show where 9 girls and 9 guys are trying to find their destiny.

name: Der Mutterbaum
summary: Kallie reveals the truth of what he saw, Sybrand and Tsedza investigate Simon's disappearance and Pattie's negligence leads to new tragedy.

show.name: Donkerbos
show.summary: When the bodies of six children are found in the backwater forests of Donkerbos, Limpopo, an ostracised detective must wrestle with her dark past, her family and a distrustful community to catch the killer before another child is taken.

show.name: Curtain Call
show.summary: A work depicting the story of a man playing as a grandson to fulfill the last wish of an elderly grandmother who defected from the North.

name: Episode 2
summary: An unexpected visitor shows up at Hye-joo's home. Assemblyman Nam Joong-do attempts to divert the public's attention from his family.

show.name: Trolley
show.summary: The secret of assemblyman Nam Joong-do who lived away from the world while hiding his past and his wife Kim Hye-joo comes out into the world, drawing the dilemma facing the couple.

show.name: I Will Be Your Bloom
show.summary: Asuka had once realized her goal to become a teacher, but after a gutting failure, she gives up her dream profession and becomes extremely withdrawn. After a series of events, she finds herself becoming a live-in housemother for a dorm... where the boy band septet 8LOOM live together! At the dorm, she is reunited with her former student Dan—as a teacher, Asuka used to encourage him to go for his dreams. Inspired by Dan's leadership in the band and his passion for making his dream come true, Asuka, too, regains the passion she had in her teaching days and comes to terms with her own failure.

name: Eun Hee's Killer
summary: The Industrial Complex Three welcomes Wook and Pan Seok. It turns out Hyun Ji had been living in the village until Pan Seok found her remains. Also, they find that Yang Eun Hee is a resident there. For Myung Ja's sake, they decide to find who killed Eun Hee and secure her body so that she may rest in peace.

show.name: Missing: The Other Side
show.summary: A village holds spirits of missing, deceased people. A search to find the missing bodies and discover the truth behind their disappearance occurs.

show.name: Inside the NFL
show.summary: Experienced, articulate and connected, the hardest-hitting team of analysts in sports delivers expert insight, exclusive commentary and special on and off the field features you won't find anywhere else. Emmy® Award-winning Inside the NFL brings you the sights, sounds and spectacle of the NFL in all its glory, including exciting player profiles, interviews, and intense, moment-by-moment game footage. Every team. Every game. Every week.

show.name: Rooster Teeth Podcast
show.summary: On a more or less weekly basis the Rooster Teeth (creators of Red vs. Blue) crew discuss gaming, films and projects that they are currently working on.

show.name: All About Android
show.summary: All About Android delivers everything you want to know about Android each week -- the biggest news, freshest hardware, best apps and geekiest how-to's -- with Android enthusiasts Jason Howell, Florence Ion, Ron Richards, and a variety of special guests along the way.

name: Mr. T and Emmanuel Lewis in A Christmas Dream

show.name: Atop the Fourth Wall
show.summary: Atop the Fourth Wall is a comic book review show, hosted by Lewis "Linkara" Lovhaug. The show specializes in reviewing really bad comic books.

show.name: Death Battle!
show.summary: Death Battle! places two or more characters from pop culture in an all out, no-holds barred slugfest to the death. Who will survive? What weapons will be used? How much blood will be spilled? Death Battle! has the answers.

name: February 31st
summary: As Steve's financial woes mount, Nick offers a lifeline in the form of a proposal that would take Chippendales global. A printing error has disastrous consequences for Steve.

show.name: Welcome to Chippendales
show.summary: A sprawling true-crime saga, Welcome to Chippendales tells the outrageous story of Somen "Steve" Banerjee, an Indian immigrant who became the unlikely founder of the world's greatest male-stripping empire - and let nothing stand in his way in the process. The series details the insane, darkly comedic, crime-ridden story behind the unique male revue that became a cultural phenomenon.

show.name: Dirty Laundry
show.summary: Host Lily Du gathers together four guests to tell secrets, guess who they belong to, and enjoy a few drinks.

name: The Messengers
summary: Marly visits Sara. Nardo returns to work at BCPD. Pete spends time with his newborn son Marlon. Evan has a close call after Avery tells him the truth. Lex stays close to Sara.

show.name: The Bay
show.summary:
THE BAY follows the affluent, yet dysfunctional Bay City residents living in a town cursed by Red Garrett, an ominous senator who was murdered by his socialite granddaughter, Sara Garrett. Living in his shadow, Sara, her son Pete, and those around them face a series of dilemmas involving rape, blackmail, sordid lovers, and vindictive arch rivals. Their lives riddled with forbidden love, malicious lies, and never-ending scandals, the town's privileged tangle with those who confuse obsession for love, vengeance for justice, and power for success.

The Bay (a.k.a. The Bay The Series) is a digital/web daytime drama series that premiered on September 15, 2010, at Blip.tv and later moved to Amazon Prime. For its sixth season, the series ran on Popstar! TV.

show.name: The Boulet Brothers' Dragula: Titans
show.summary: Hosted by The Boulet Brothers, this spin-off series of The Boulet Brothers' Dragula stars monster drag artists from the show's previous seasons returning to the competition for a chance to win a $100,000 grand prize and the title of Dragula's first Titan. Each week the returning drag monsters must compete in makeup, costume creation, and performance based challenges to prove that they are the best of the best, while the weakest among them must face terrifying physical feats or risk elimination until only the true Titan of Dragula remains.

name: A Beautiful Mess
summary: Tara and Percy renovate the cluttered living room of their farmhouse.

show.name: The Story of Home
show.summary: Tara and Percy are interior designers with a passion for old homes. After years of designing for others, now they're taking on a live-in renovation for their own farmhouse in upstate New York.

name: Episode 10
summary: As the ultimate psychological reality show continues, and the number of players keeps on dwindling, another faithful does not make it to breakfast - but who has been murdered? During the mission, the players require laser focus to add more gold to the life-changing prize pot. And with paranoia and tensions reaching boiling point, the game is dramatically turned on its head, sending shock waves around the castle.

show.name: The Traitors
show.summary: Nail-biting psychological competition where 22 strangers play the ultimate reality game of detection, backstabbing and trust, in the hope of winning up to £120,000.

show.name: Are You the One?
show.summary: 21 singles ask themselves the question: Are you the one? Only when all candidates have found their "perfect match" do they win a sum of 200,000 euros together.

show.name: WWE NXT
show.summary: Each Wednesday at 8:00 p.m. ET, WWE Superstars and Divas of tomorrow face off on WWE NXT, a one-hour weekly show that features the brightest and best of WWE's rising stars. WWE NXT showcases the Superstars and Divas from WWE's Performance Center as well as appearances from WWE Superstars and Legends in an intimate setting. WWE NXT broadcasts from the state-of-the-art Full Sail LIVE venue on the Full Sail University in campus in Orlando, Florida.
